      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-cared for over the years! It's perfect for someone looking for a solid, dependable car that still looks great on the road. I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale to a good home, so come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it drives! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
