      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features the 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission with Drivelogic, providing seamless torque delivery and lightning-fast shifts. The chassis remains composed thanks to Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a factory M Variable Differential Lock that ensures optimal power distribution across the rear axle. Maintenance is up to date, with particular attention paid to the throttle actuators and fluid intervals. The vehicle retains its sharp turn-in and visceral induction roar, presenting as a solid example for the driver who prioritizes engineering excellence and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
