    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the ideal balance between everyday utility and premium comfort. Meticulously maintained by a non-smoker, the interior remains in excellent shape with supple upholstery and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment and climate control systems\u2014functioning perfectly. The exterior finish holds a deep gloss, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips one would expect from careful road use. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has a complete service history, recently passed a comprehensive safety inspection, and just received a fresh oil service and new brake pads. It tracks straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without the need for upcoming maintenance.",
