    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It's in really lovely shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. It drives like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway! If you're looking for a reliable, happy car that's ready for many more road trips, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
